==English==

===Interjection===
'''Oh, no'''

# an exclamation or expression of [[alarm]], [[concern]], or [[resentment]] about a problem or [[error]]
#: '''''Oh, no'''! The rug is on fire!''
#: '''''Oh, no'''! Did I leave my keys in the car?''

